### Session CRUD API Tests
### Tests for SessionCrudController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### List all sessions
### Returns list of all AI sessions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new session
### Creates a new AI session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": "opencode",
  "model": "glm-4.7"
}

###

### Get session by ID
### Returns details of a specific session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Delete session
### Deletes a specific session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Initialize session
### Initializes a session with specific configuration
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}/init
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": "opencode",
  "model": "glm-4.7",
  "prompt": "Hello, how can you help me?"
}

###
